<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَرَأَيْتَ}</span> ... أَلَا تَعْجَبُ!!<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَتَوَلَّى}</span> ... أَعْرَضَ عَنِ الإِيمَانِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
